) vs 260 dmg DD (+7 second cast time) for the Shamans on a LOWER level armor piece, I think that it's wholly understandable to upgrade to a spell that does 650 dmg over 60 seconds instead.</p>&nbsp;<br><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>Virale Rahien`Sorei<br>Level 47 Druid of E'ci<br>Master Brewer and Jeweler</td></tr>
